cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.IR, cs.MM

The paper proposes a system that uses convolutional neural networks for limited angle CT reconstruction, which falls under computer vision (cs.CV) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The use of neural networks also suggests machine learning (cs.LG) as a possible sub-category. The paper also mentions analytical and iterative reconstruction techniques, which fall under information retrieval (cs.IR). Finally, the paper discusses the preservation of 3D structure, which suggests multimedia (cs.MM) as a possible sub-category.
